3. Nearest nested `AGENTS.md` for the folder under edit

## Philosophy (do not restate in code)

- Polymorphic collapse over parallel types/helpers; one entrypoint per concern
- Effect-first / ROP: `Fin`, `Validation`, `Eff`; typed errors; no exception control flow in domain
- External-lib-first: approved packages are the implementation surface; no thin wrappers
- Greenfield: break APIs freely; no shims, `[Obsolete]`, or compatibility aliases
- Concept-density trigger (not LOC): ≥3 parallel types, sibling factories, switch arms, or single-call helpers → collapse in place

## Quality gates (orthogonal — never merge)

| Rail | Command |
|------|---------|
| Static C# | `bash scripts/check-cs.sh check` |
| Full static (trigger files only) | `bash scripts/check-cs.sh full` |
| Unit tests | `bash scripts/test.sh [<filter>]` |
| Rhino runtime | `bash scripts/rhino.sh verify <scenario-or-glob>` |

Trust CSP#### analyzer rules in `tools/cs-analyzer` — fix architecture, do not suppress.

